This directory
  es

standing for
  "execution state"

stores task controller execution state so that it may be
restored in the event of a crash.

Generally, every queue, short, long or test, will requires it own state files.

== State Files ==

sq_peu    Short queue previously executing user.
sq_ceu    Short queue currently executing user.

lq_peu    Long queue previously executing user.
lq_ceu    Long queue currently executing user.
